Conclusion: When faced with 4...Bc5 5.0-0 0-0, the energetic 6.Nxe5 is a
superior option to 6.d3. It isn't necessary to recover the piece quickly, and
it can even be a mistake. With a symmetrical center, the resource f4-f5 is
gaining space and is the key in White's plan.} *

