$1 Bf5 21. Rd1 $18 {0-1 Rublevsky,S (2665)-Sokolov,I (2685)/Poikovsky 2006}) (
9... Qe7 10. Re1 {Transposes to Chapter IX.}) ({The direct} 9... g5 $6 {
is dubious. It's similar to the lines seen in 9...Kh8?!.} 10. Nxg5 {More
adequate is:} Nxe4 (10... hxg5 $2 {Leads to a lost position for Black.} 11.
