14... Bc6 15. Re1 Qe7 16. Qd3 (16. Qc1 {Has also been played.} Kh8 17. Qa3 Rfe8
18. d5 Bd7 19. Qa5 g5 20. Bg3 $13 {1/2-1/2 (37) Zarnicki,P (2515)-Slipak,S  
