to complicate the game with:} 24. f6 $2 {is counterproductive.} gxf6 25. Nxh6
Nef3+ $19) 24... Qxe5 25. Qxe5 Nf3+ 26. Kf2 Nxe5 27. Bf4 {With an endgame
