} Nb6 (19... c4 20. f4 Nc5 21. f5 g5 22. Ng2 $18 {[%csl Gh4][%cal Gh2h4]}) 20.
a4 $1 Qg7 21. a5 Qxh6 22. Bxh6 Nbd7 23. Nf3 $16 {[%cal Gf3d2,Gd2c4] With a
