Be6 12. Nf5 $1 Bxc4 $6 (12... Bxf5 $2 13. Rxf5 Rf8 (13... Ne7 $4 14. Rxf6 $1
gxf6 15. Qh5 $18 {[%csl Rf6,Rf7,Rg8,Rh6][%cal Ga1f1]}) 14. Qf3 $16 {With a big
