13. Nh4 $1 {As in the previous example, all of White's play is on the f-file
and the h4-knight is about to land on the f5-square.} Ne8 $2 {This is an error
that leads to a very unpleasant position. Black's problem is that he must play
extremely precise just to hold the position.} ({The right move for Black was:} 
