threats on the kingside.}) 15. Raf1 Kh8 16. Qh3 Qb6 {[%cal Gb6e3,Gb6b2] At
least Black activated the queen.} ({A serious mistake would be:} 16... Qd7 $4
17. Rxf6 $1 gxf6 18. Nf5 $1 Nxf5 19. exf5 Ree8 20. Qxh6+ Kg8 21. Ne4 $18) 17.
Nd1 d5 $5 18. Nf5 $1 {[%csl Rg7,Rh6][%cal Gf5h6,Gf5g7]} Nxf5 19. exf5 {Again,
